      <p class="sectiontitle">INTRODUCTION</p>
      <h4 class="sectiondesc">Hi, I'm Dan.</h4>
      <p class="sectioncontent">I'm a 15 year old from Country Antrim, in Northern Ireland 🇬🇧.</p>
      <p class="sectioncontent">I'm currently in my GCSE stage of British secondary education, where I'm taking exam
        classes in Business & Communication Systems, Digital Technology, Double-Award Science, English Language +
        Literature, Further Mathematics and Geography.</p>
      <p class="sectioncontent">In the near future I hope to continue my education journey through A-levels, and
        possibly studying at university in either Finland or Norway - where I want to immigrate to when I'm an adult.
      </p>
      <p class="sectioncontent">Since creating my first basic HTML website at age 7, I've been dedicated to improving my
        skills with developing websites, apps, APIs and pretty much anything that interests me - nothing is too big of a
        challenge to even try!
      <p>

        <img src="/img/1711.jpg" id="introimg2">

    </div>

