      <h4 class="sectiondesc">Videography & photography.</h4>
      <p class="sectioncontent">Ever since 2014, I've been creating and editing YouTube videos for <a
          href="https://youtube.com/dandabsMC">my channel</a>.</p>
      <p class="sectioncontent">This love of directing, editing and scriptwriting for videos and productions has stuck
